ygData.messageBody:
But it will take me long to stay inside town nuke myself, cast spells, bind
wound, swim in pool, make brews, do smithing etc...lvl is one thing, all
these sub-skills is another pain ;(

Worst of all, I cannot be so ya-ya like now (jeeze, imagine, Ziltus Hill in
CB, hehe).

Ziltus Planeswalker
